WEBVTT

00:02.900 --> 00:09.716
This is Deborah Beale interviewing Mr. Don Feltz 
on the history of the Texas Engineering

00:02.900 --> 00:09.716
Experiment Station. The date is June 14, 1984.

00:37.409 --> 00:40.413
