now how you came to A&M? Okay, your question was how

00:43.137 --> 00:46.041
did I get associated with A&M. Okay, I was first a 
student here in 1951, and stayed here two years

00:46.842 --> 01:01.422
until I was drafted into the Army because of the 
Korean War, and then I did not get back to A&M until

00:46.842 --> 01:01.422
1957. I continued my studies toward a degree in 
mechanical engineering. And then that was

01:08.392 --> 01:15.701
followed by my immediate entry into graduate 
school as a nuclear engineer. At the time I

01:16.883 --> 01:27.155
