department, and they brought a director to the

03:41.300 --> 04:00.705
Science Center, changed the title from head to 
director, and that was Dr. John Randall. And I was

04:01.715 --> 04:05.359
named the assistant at that time, in 1965. So I've 
had just about all the jobs that are available out

04:06.801 --> 04:13.509
here since that time. And then later, I was named 
the associate director to the center.

